    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_ad.00111_large.jpg" type="recto"/>  
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">
                        <handShift rend="printed"/>
                        U.A WOODBURY PROP.
                    </name>
                    <name type="place">Van Ness and American Hotels</name>
                    <name type="place">L.S. DREW</name>
                    <name type="place">H.N. CLARK</name>
                    <name type="place">MANAGERS</name>
                    <name type="place">Burlington Vermont.</name>
                    <name type="place">Van Ness House</name>
                    <name type="place">
                        The Van Ness House has a Safety Hydraulic Passenger Elevator Fire Escape and the Grinell Automatic Sprinkler
                        <lb/>
                        Fine Views of the Lakes and Mountains from all parts of the House.
                    </name>
                    <name type="place">Burlington Vt.</name>
                    <date when="1890-12-08">
                        <handShift rend="manuscript"/>
                        Dec—8, 1890.
                    </date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Bro Walt,</salute> 
            </opener>
            <p>
                I wrote last time that Han<ptr target="n7033"/> was better
                The prevailing severe cold weather at present retards her
                convalescence a little—dreadful cold, and the character,
                or effect of the atmostphere almost neutralizes all the warmth
                that might be obtained from the hottest coal fire—It makes
                me very apprehensive—</p>
            <p>
                I hope you are as well, or
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_ad.00112_large.jpg" type="verso"/>  
                comfortable as when last you wrote—Small book
                rec<hi rend="underline">d</hi></p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Gratefully Yours,</salute>
                <signed>Charlie</signed>
            </closer> 
            <postscript>
                <p>
                    Time stagnant, in every thing
                </p>
            </postscript>
        </body>
    </text> 
